{"word":"G2335 - θεωρία - theōría - theh-o-ree'-ah - Sight","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεωρία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">theōría</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">theh-o-ree'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sight</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"காட்சி - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. a viewing, beholding"},{"paragraph":"2. that which is viewed; a spectacle, sight"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2334 - θεωρέω - theōréō - theh-o-reh'-o/2334\">G2334</a>; <i>spectatorship</i>, that is, (concretely) a <i>spectacle:</i> - sight.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}